text: Mostly for my Saturday long run, since there is a huge park with easily \~15 miles of trails about a 10 minute drive from home. Absolutely worth it for the amazing scenery when I'm going to be spending 90+ minutes running, makes it much more tolerable than sidewalks and roads.

There is another one planned for February in a couple weeks: https://facebook.com/events/s/pain-in-the-yeahs-community-wi/1272788726442280/?ti=icl
